sequenceDiagram
    participant Op as Operator
    participant CatalogAPI as Catalog API
    participant ProductDomain as Product Domain
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant Orders as orders BC

    Op ->> CatalogAPI: PATCH /products/{id}/price
    CatalogAPI ->> ProductDomain: updatePrice(newPrice)
    ProductDomain ->> ProductDomain: verify CAT-RULE-002 (not DISCONTINUED)
    ProductDomain ->> ProductDomain: create PriceHistory entry (CAT-RULE-009)
    ProductDomain ->> ProductDomain: update price field
    ProductDomain -->> CatalogAPI: OK
    CatalogAPI ->> MQ: publish ProductPriceChanged (catalog.product.price-changed)
    MQ ->> Orders: ProductPriceChanged consumed - updates CatalogSnapshot price
    CatalogAPI -->> Op: 204 No Content
